<HEAD>Dukakis Works On New York, Pennsylvania Primaries</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By TED DUNCOMBE</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>SWARTHMORE, Pa. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
