coming months. However, <PERSON> Blanchard </PERSON> said he would not permit the platform hearings to turn into an ideological battleground. `` I'd like to think that someone will read it other than opponents. I hate to work on something that will collect dust,'' <PERSON> Blanchard </PERSON> said.
