<HEAD>Defendants Acquitted of All Charges in Sedition Trial</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By BILL SIMMONS</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>FORT SMITH, Ark. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
