year. The <ORGANIZATION> NYSE </ORGANIZATION>'s composite index of all its listed common stocks added .68 to 150.44. At the <ORGANIZATION> American </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Stock </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Exchange </ORGANIZATION>, the market value index was up 1.12 at 298.70. Volume on the <ORGANIZATION> Big </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Board </ORGANIZATION> came to 153.42 million shares with an hour to go.
